        <updateDate>2008-06-10T21:05:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Schools in Homeland Security Planning Act of 2008 - Amends the Homeland Security Act of 2002 to condition the receipt of certain state homeland security grants on a state including a representative of the state department of education in each homeland security decision-making body of the state that has authority to determine how such grants will be used. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
